bio: 1. Years is a project from Ohad Benchetrit of Sphyr, Do Make Say Think and Broken Social Scene. The self-titled album is due to be released on Arts & Crafts on May 5, 2009. "You work off of inspiration and while you let it flow into tracks it becomes a diary and that entry becomes a piece of history. If you are ever inclined to remind yourself of who you were, you put it on, listen to it and go ‘oh yeah!’. Sometimes it might make you smile or laugh and sometimes it might make you cringe—but it will always be a marker for who you were. Read more on Last.fm
